commit.message:
avr.c (final_prescan_insn): Remove support for -mrtl.

	* config/avr/avr.c (final_prescan_insn): Remove support for
	-mrtl.
	* config/avr/avr.h (MASK_RTL_DUMP): Remove.
	(TARGET_RTL_DUMP): Likewise.
	(TARGET_SWITCHES): Remove -mrtl.

From-SVN: r68530
